com.singularity.ee.connectors.entity.api
Interface IOSTypedPropertyDefinition

All Known Implementing Classes:
OSTypedPropertyDefinition
public interface IOSTypedPropertyDefinition

This wrapper object allows a property definition to be associated with a specific OS type. A null OS type means that the property definition applies to any OS type. When setting the OS type, use one of the constants specified in IImage.
